_sText:
Extended version of de_aztec by valve.

FINAL VERSION RELEASED - de_aztec_ukcs_extended

AIM: Stop stalemate that is created by original
de_aztec.

BETA_v6:
Added nav mesh to allow bot players.
General optimizing.
Adjusted architecture of new Waterway to give more cover.

BETA_v5:
Added vent near to bombsite B.
Increased size of hole in wall in the new section near bridge.
FPS increased to same standard as original de_aztec.

BETA_v4:
Fixed known texture errors (nodraw etc.)
Added radar overview.

BETA_v3:
FPS increased 3* from earlier release.
Architecture adjusted.
Textures changed to avoid displacement faults - will be improved for final release.

BETA_v1/v2 :
added shortcuts at CT spawn.
added bypass from waterway upto bridge via ladder.
added tunnel from T spawn to bombsite B to bypass double doors.
added tunnel from T waterway to bombsite B as extra route.
added tunnel from T side of bridge to CT side of bridge through mountain.

Now working on BETA_v7

All feedback is welcomed especially cons as it helps me to improve the map :)
